videos.description: Julius Randle elevates and slaps Russell Westbrook's layup attempt off the glass to set up a Knicks fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Randle spanks Westbrook's layup off the glass) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randle spanks Westbrook's layup off the glass

videos.description: LeBron James tosses up a high lob and Anthony Davis extends to grab it and hammer it home for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron connects with AD on the alley-oop) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron connects with AD on the alley-oop

videos.description: RJ Barrett uses a series of moves and good footwork to fool Russell Westbrook and get an easy open shot inside.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (RJ Barrett gets crafty for a bucket on Westbrook) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: RJ Barrett gets crafty for a bucket on Westbrook

videos.description: RJ Barrett gets the hoop and the harm

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (RJ Barrett gets the hoop and the harm) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: RJ Barrett gets the hoop and the harm

videos.description: Anthony Davis comes streaking in to grab the miss and flushes a dunk with authority on Mitchell Robinson.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD flies in for putback slam on Robinson) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD flies in for putback slam on Robinson

videos.description: Julius Randle throws down a nice fast-break dunk then Nerlens Noel shuts down Malik Monk's layup attempt on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Knicks stick it to Lakers with must see dunk and block) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Knicks stick it to Lakers with must see dunk and block

videos.description: Anthony Davis takes a shot in the face from LeBron James' arm as he goes in for a second-chance tip-in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron pops AD in the jaw on putback bucket) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron pops AD in the jaw on putback bucket

videos.description: Malik Monk tosses an alley-oop behind him to Anthony Davis who skies for the emphatic slam dunk on the break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Monk lobs behind him to AD for the slam) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Monk lobs behind him to AD for the slam

videos.description: Russell Westbrook forces a Knicks turnover then Malik Monk gets the ball in the corner for a fast-break 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lakers outwork Knicks for huge fast-break 3) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lakers outwork Knicks for huge fast-break 3

videos.description: The fans in Crypto.com Arena rain down boos at Russell Westbrook after he badly misses a bank shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook hears the 'boos' after clanking badly) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook hears the 'boos' after clanking badly

videos.description: Alec Burks uses a 'take foul' in the open court that stops LeBron James' epic reverse dunk from counting.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's epic dunk waved off by Burks' take foul) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's epic dunk waved off by Burks' take foul

videos.description: Spike Lee sinks in his seat after LeBron James takes on two Knicks to score a tough layup off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's bucket has Spike Lee sinking in his seat) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's bucket has Spike Lee sinking in his seat

videos.description: RJ Barrett blows by Russell Westbrook for a huge dunk, then gets called for delay of game after he swats down LeBron James' inbound pass.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (RJ Barrett gets delay of game after huge dunk) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: RJ Barrett gets delay of game after huge dunk

videos.description: LeBron James comes up with the loose ball and races down the court to hammer home a dunk with emphasis.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron crams down emphatic fast-break slam in OT) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron crams down emphatic fast-break slam in OT

videos.description: Anthony Davis gets the ball on the fast break and stuffs down an easy dunk as the Lakers increase their lead to 122-115 over the Knicks in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD puts finishing touches on win vs. Knicks with fast-break slam in OT) 2022/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD puts finishing touches on win vs. Knicks with fast-break slam in OT

videos.description: Lakers defeat the Knicks in overtime after a huge triple-double showing from LeBron James and solid performances by Anthony Davis and Malik Monk.
